=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d48ef0fdea1ccbca71d350e96438bf9af235cec","tid":1478624,"uid":35084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓主認真？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign</span>"},{"pid":"948ccee6f1dd887bbd83d502214ae20282eb9a0e","tid":1478624,"uid":278283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"BNO持有人可簽"},{"pid":"77b55f392d899d724a90795cc2de1b7b9119ca6d","tid":1478624,"uid":207094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7734f3a0aecddd056dc4fd7ff93168c2fc54502","tid":1478624,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0fYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=e81307aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> / 英國佬唔會幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Q2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ4: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0fYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=e81307aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"dc4c60e7f5b368923d996a0b655c242278d9d536","tid":1478624,"uid":189961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d48ef0fdea1ccbca71d350e96438bf9af235cec","tid":1478624,"uid":35084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓主認真？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"A: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\n其實都係for夠多人簽先有機會擺上枱討論je 佢應該唔會要你sd副本證明比佢地睇 \b同埋如上面所說 都係比佢地多條後路去盡情抗爭 幫得就幫 我都冇bno 照簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 想問下隻豬仔舉818個圖案點先打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a9dc45d35f9b19d1505d3b28c52e43aaf8ec7d","tid":1478624,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc4c60e7f5b368923d996a0b655c242278d9d536","tid":1478624,"uid":189961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d48ef0fdea1ccbca71d350e96438bf9af235cec","tid":1478624,"uid":35084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"樓主認真？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"A: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\n其實都係for夠多人簽先有機會擺上枱討論je 佢應該唔會要你sd副本證明比佢地睇 \b同埋如上面所說 都係比佢地多條後路去盡情抗爭 幫得就幫 我都冇bno 照簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 想問下隻豬仔舉818個圖案點先打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci